headline: United Airlines Holdings Inc. (UAL) Settles on GEnx engines for New 787 Dreamliners, Brazil Okays $100M Azul Investment
summary: United Airlines Holdings Inc. (NASDAQ:UAL) is one of the high-growth industrial stocks to buy. On February 16, United Airlines Holdings Inc. (NASDAQ:UAL) selected 300 GEnx engines to power its new 787 Dreamliners.
